{"id":8804,"date":"2026-02-03T10:10:34","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:10:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8804"},"modified":"2026-02-03T13:43:40","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T06:43:40","slug":"glutathione-chong-oxy-hoa-va-lam-sang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/glutathione-chong-oxy-hoa-va-lam-sang\/","title":{"rendered":"Glutathione \u2013 Ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cmaster antioxidant\u201d (ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y), Glutathione kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i stress oxy ho\u00e1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-glutathione\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Glutathione<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: L-Glutathione (\u03b3-L-glutamyl-L-cysteinylglycine).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t: L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tripeptide t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb ba acid amin \u2013 cysteine, glutamic acid v\u00e0 glycine.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: C\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft t\u1ebf b\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf gan, gi\u00fap th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng oxy ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: Glutathione \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o sau stress UV.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: Reduced Glutathione, GSH.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8808 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Glutathione\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-glutathione\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Glutathione<\/b><b><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh: trung ho\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do (ROS), b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do tia UV, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m ho\u1eb7c stress n\u1ed9i sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da: \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase, gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p melanin t\u1ed1i (eumelanin) v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang melanin s\u00e1ng (pheomelanin), gi\u00fap da s\u00e1ng trong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: gi\u00fap vitamin C v\u00e0 E t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1ea1i sau khi b\u1ecb oxy ho\u00e1, k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glutathione t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf hai d\u1ea1ng: kh\u1eed (GSH) v\u00e0 oxy ho\u00e1 (GSSG). Trong t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, GSH ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, gi\u00fap trung ho\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng oxy ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da, GSH t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean men tyrosinase trong t\u1ebf b\u00e0o melanocyte, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p melanin s\u1eadm m\u00e0u v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Serum, essence, cream:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u1ee9a Glutathione ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c d\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t tan trong n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 Glutathione disulfide, S-acetyl glutathione.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng\/ti\u00eam y khoa:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c (kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea1m vi m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ho\u1eb7c ampoule:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> d\u00f9ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n, th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng vitamin C, niacinamide, tranexamic acid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-glutathione\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Glutathione<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, th\u00e2m n\u00e1m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n oxy ho\u00e1 nh\u01b0 n\u1eafng, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang treatment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, k\u00e9m \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng an to\u00e0n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8809 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-3.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Glutathione\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-dung-%e2%80%93-lieu-luong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng \u2013 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glutathione b\u00f4i: n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng 1\u20132 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y trong serum ho\u1eb7c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. Khi d\u00f9ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c, n\u00ean thoa sau vitamin C ho\u1eb7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng serum s\u00e1ng da c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a GSH, c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u <\/span><b>4\u20136 tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 Glutathione trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb 0,1\u20132%, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8908\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8908\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8908 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Glutathione.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3ng g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng glutathione trong c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Glutathione.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Glutathione-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Glutathione-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/Glutathione-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8908\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3ng g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng glutathione trong c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glutathione u\u1ed1ng: c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng b\u1ed5 sung 500-2400mg GSH k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p L-cystine \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-glutathione-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Glutathione sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Glutathione + Vitamin C:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Glutathione + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng b\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Glutathione + Tranexamic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ng\u0103n n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da s\u1ea1m do n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Glutathione + Hyaluronic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap da t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Glutathione + Retinol (lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1nh b\u00f4i c\u00f9ng l\u00fac n\u1ebfu da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-trang-giga-gsc\/\">Serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng GIGA GSC<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-glutathione\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh Glutathione<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glutathione an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t \u1edf h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ng\u1ee9a nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch tho\u00e1ng qua khi m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 serum c\u00f3 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u1edbi acid m\u1ea1nh (AHA\/BHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao) trong c\u00f9ng b\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00ec m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng acid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a GSH.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng u\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c ti\u00eam y khoa, c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u2013 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 d\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8810\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8810\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8810 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-4.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Glutathione kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Glutathione-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8810\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Glutathione kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00f4i thoa. Glutathione l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i sinh c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, an to\u00e0n khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u00eam ho\u1eb7c vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng li\u1ec1u cao khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-bao-quan-glutathione\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n Glutathione<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glutathione r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 oxy, n\u00ean c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n trong chai t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u, k\u00edn kh\u00ed v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 d\u01b0\u1edbi 30\u00b0C.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Sau khi m\u1edf n\u1eafp, n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong 3\u20136 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u1ebfu serum \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u (v\u00e0ng, n\u00e2u) ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 m\u00f9i sulfur, n\u00ean ng\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Alzahrani, T. F., Alotaibi, S. M., Alzahrani, A. A., Alzahrani, A. F., Alturki, L. E., Alshammari, M. M., Alharbi, R. A., Alanazi, S. I., Alshammari, W. Z., &amp; Algarni, A. S. (2025). Exploring the Safety and Efficacy of Glutathione Supplementation for Skin Lightening: A Narrative Review. Cureus, 17(1). <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.7759\/cureus.78045\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.7759\/cureus.78045<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Glutathione \u2013 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 n\u1ed9i sinh, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8807,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8804","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8804","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8804"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8804\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8919,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8804\/revisions\/8919"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8807"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8804"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8804"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8804"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}